    {
        "id":"waterway_forest_isolated_man",
        "message":"What are you doing in my house?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I've come a long distance in the pursuit of my brother Andor. So I peeked inside to see if he was in here.",
                "nextPhraseID":"waterway_forest_isolated_man_5",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"andor_ending",
                        "value":900,
                        "negate":true
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"I am looking for someone that could explain why that land nearby is strange.",
                "nextPhraseID":"waterway_forest_isolated_man_5",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"poisonland",
                        "value":25,
                        "negate":true
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"I heard about the Battle of Brightport in a lecture at the academy, but your nephew Eiden said most of what we learnt is false. He directed me here to hear the real story from you.",
                "nextPhraseID":"poisonland_isolatedman",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"poisonland",
                        "value":25,
                        "negate":false
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"I was looking for help in getting into that cave just west of here.",
                "nextPhraseID":"poisonland_isolatedman0",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"questProgress",
                        "requireID":"nondisplay",
                        "value":46,
                        "negate":true
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"waterway_forest_isolated_man_5",
        "message":"Do you really think that I believe that? Who are you, what do you really want?!",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Can you just answer my question?",
